class.comment: Represents an Object that can be represented in @(string) form.

PRE_BUILT_MAP_THRESHOLD.comment: The threshold for a pre-built generated map for converting an object to a string.

return.comment: The serialized name of this object.

getSerializedName.comment: Fetches the serialized name of this object.

params.name: supplier
params.comment: The supplier of the array of objects.

fromEnum.comment: Generates an @({this}$EnumCodec) from a supplier for an array of serializable enums.

params.name: supplier
params.comment: The supplier of the array of objects.

params.name: mapper
params.comment: The function to convert @({this}#getSerializedName) into another string.

E.comment: The enumeration that implements this class.

keys.comment: Fetches the keys from an array of @({this})s.
